1.70.0 ¬∑ [source](https://doc.rust-lang.org/1.80.0/src/core/result.rs.html#584)

Returns `true` if the result is [`Ok`](about:blank/std/result/enum.Result.html#variant.Ok "variant std::result::Result::Ok") and the value inside of it matches a predicate.

##### [¬ß](#examples-1-2)Examples

```
let x: Result<u32, &str> = Ok(2);
assert_eq!(x.is_ok_and(|x| x > 1), true);

let x: Result<u32, &str> = Ok(0);
assert_eq!(x.is_ok_and(|x| x > 1), false);

let x: Result<u32, &str> = Err("hey");
assert_eq!(x.is_ok_and(|x| x > 1), false);
```

