Converts from `Result<T, E>` to [`Option<T>`](../../std/option/enum.Option.html "enum std::option::Option").

Converts `self` into an [`Option<T>`](../../std/option/enum.Option.html "enum std::option::Option"), consuming `self`, and discarding the error, if any.

##### [¬ß](#examples-4-5)Examples

```
let x: Result<u32, &str> = Ok(2);
assert_eq!(x.ok(), Some(2));

let x: Result<u32, &str> = Err("Nothing here");
assert_eq!(x.ok(), None);
```

