##### [¬ß](#recommended-message-style)Recommended Message Style

We recommend that `expect` messages are used to describe the reason you _expect_ the `Result` should be `Ok`.

[‚ìò](# "This example panics")

```
let path = std::env::var("IMPORTANT_PATH")
    .expect("env variable `IMPORTANT_PATH` should be set by `wrapper_script.sh`");
```

